# For details of the following setting, see
# https://vxlabs.com/2021/03/21/mbsync-copyarrivaldate-yes/
CopyArrivalDate yes

IMAPAccount migadu
Host imap.migadu.com
User david@daporter.net
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/Mail/migadu.gpg"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore migadu
Account migadu

MaildirStore local
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel primary
Far :migadu:
Near :local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
